Name: TwoSpeedAxleSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates the current axle range.

Name: ParkingBrakeSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates when the parking brake is set.

Name: CruiseCtrlPauseSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates the position of the Cruise Control Pause Switch used on Remote Cruise Control applications.

Name: CruiseControlState
Comment: This parameter is used to indicate the current state, or mode, of operation by the cruise control device. This is a status parameter.

Name: EngIdleIncrementSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates the position of the idle increment switch.

Name: EngIdleDecrementSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates the position of the idle decrement switch.

Name: EngTestModeSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates the position of the engine test mode switch.

Name: EngShutdownOverrideSwitch
Comment: Switch signal which indicates the position of the engine shutdown override switch.
